      <strong>What’s in the box? You’ll never guess.</strong>
      That’s what our good friend Matt told us as he recounted a salacious story about the time his movers almost found his and his partner’s strangest sex toy. <strong>“It’s the most incriminating thing I own, and it’s nothing like you’ve ever seen,”</strong> he said with a smile.
