      <br><br>
      Frustrated, we gave up. But we still wondered. Over the years, we’ve asked many others what they think it could be, and we’ve gotten answers ranging from hilarious to awe-inspiring to downright twisted.
      <br><br>
      According to Matt, we still haven’t guessed correctly. But in posing this question to our friends, we realized that people have some pretty cool ideas. The conversation became less about what was actually in the box and more about what could be in the box. That is, if it existed. We learned that there are tons of toys that people can dream up, but that aren’t real. Yet.
    </p>
  </div>

